OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChelsea FC owner Roman     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FAbramovich gets apology    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fover Putin claim           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Russian billionaire Roman Abramovich   
OL,6, has received an apology from a         
OL,7, publisher over defamatory allegations. 
OL,9,FHarperCollins published a book which   
OL,10,Fincluded the claim that Mr Abramovich  
OL,11,Fbought London football club Chelsea on 
OL,12,Fthe orders of Russia's President       
OL,13,FVladimir Putin.                        
OL,15,FOn Wednesday the company apologised to 
OL,16,FMr Abramovich and confirmed it had     
OL,17,Freached a settlement.                  
OL,19,FIt has amended the book, Putin's People
OL,20,Fby UK journalist Catherine Belton.     
